information: The company FRITZ WINTER EISENGIESSEREI GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1951, which operates in the Iron, special grade and pig iron industry. It also operates in the manufacture of brake discs, industrial vehicle brake discs, Cylinder heads, and Vehicle brake components and elements industries. It is based in Stadtallendorf, Germany.
